BULKY_PRODUCT_HOME_DELIVERY.pricing: Ceny jsou uvedeny pro hmotnost do 5kg. Pro těžší zásilky může být cena v košíku uvedena jiná.

SUMMARY: DELIVERY OPTIONS: Fyft.cz offers three main delivery methods for the Czech Republic: Home delivery via GLS, delivery to Zásilkovna parcel shops, and free in-store pickup in Prague. PRICING: GLS home delivery costs 95 Kč. Zásilkovna parcel shops cost 69 Kč. In-store pickup is free. There is no mention of a free shipping threshold. DELIVERY TIMES: GLS delivers the next working day. Zásilkovna delivers in 1-3 working days. Orders placed before 8:00 AM are dispatched the same day. NOTABLE FEATURES: Cash on delivery (COD) is available for a surcharge of 40 Kč for GLS and 20 Kč for Zásilkovna. There is no specific service for bulky items, but the site notes that shipping costs for items over 5kg may be higher. Weekend delivery is not available. Parcel lockers are not mentioned as a distinct option. WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is presented clearly and concisely on a dedicated 'Doprava' page. Prices, delivery times, and COD fees are easy to find for each available option. The information is well-organized and sufficient for making a decision.
